value.title: Biden and Cunningham Hold Slim Leads in North Carolina, Poll Finds
value.excerpt: Joe Biden and Cal Cunningham both led their Republican rivals by three points, a Times/Siena College survey found. Perhaps most notably, 64 percent of respondents said they had already voted.

value.title: Top Democrat says Trump administration moving ahead with sale of F-35 jets to the UAE

value.title: Trump is taking credit for the 'biggest and best' GDP  in American history. Here are the facts
value.excerpt: The US government just published an eye-popping report: Gross domestic product, the broadest measure of the country's economic growth, grew at a stunning 33.1% annual rate in the third quarter.

value.title: Wisconsin GOP says hackers stole $2.3M from Trump reelection fund
value.excerpt: Hackers stole $2.3 million from the Wisconsin Republican Party's account that was being used to help reelect President Donald Trump in the key battleground state, the party's chairman told The Associated Press on Thursday.

value.title: Watch: Trump rushes Sen. Martha McSally on stage during Arizona rally
value.excerpt: During a campaign rally in Goodyear, Ariz., President Donald Trump rushed Republican Senator Martha McSally on stage to speak. McSally is in a close Senate race with her Democratic challenger astronaut Mark Kelly.

value.title: Judge rejects DOJ's attempt to defend Trump in E. Jean Carroll rape defamation lawsuit
value.excerpt: A federal judge on Tuesday denied the Justice Department's effort to intervene in a defamation lawsuit brought against President Donald Trump by a longtime magazine columnist who has alleged he raped her, paving the way for the case to proceed.
